word: VISITED SUMMER HILL, SYDNEY, ASHFIELD, AND NEWTOWN AGAIN IN AUGUST, SPEAKING AND COUNSELING, AND SPENT A FEW DAYS IN SUMMER HILL IN SEPT.  SPOKE FREQUENTLY TO THE STUDENTS, AND ON SABBATHS "IN THE CROWDED UPPER CHAMBER."  OCT. 16 SPOKE IN THE NEW CHAPEL, AND OCT. 17 OFFERED DEDICATORY PRAYER AT THE DEDICATION OF THE NEW CHAPEL--A TRIUMPH OF FAITH.
